Nigerian celebrity couple, Simi and Adekunle Gold have welcomed their first child. Simi confirmed the news on her Instagram verified page. The ‘Duduke’ singer shared a picture of her husband, Adekunle gold holding the new baby. Alongside the picture, she wrote: “Adejare, It’s like free-falling – this unending, soul snatching, infinite, mind-boggling love. “Deja, my baby girl, I got you. I promise. Now and forever. So help me God.5.30.2020.” DAILY POST recalls that the couple secretly got engaged in December 2018 and got married sometime in January 2019.